data.description: Welcome home to your secluded oasis in the prestigious Summerlin community of Regency, where luxury and comfort blend seamlessly! Nestled behind guarded gates, this single-story haven boasts an unrivaled elegance and an array of resort-style amenities that redefine gracious living. This single-story Toll Brothers home exudes elegance and offers resort-style amenities. Step into a refined space adorned with high-end finishes. The backyard is an entertainer's dream with a custom grill, enchanting fountain, and relaxing spa under the Summerlin skies. This residence on a premium lot is more than a home—it's an experience of comfort and luxury. Enjoy access to an award-winning clubhouse and resort like amenities for elevated living. Built in 2017, this contemporary masterpiece combines modern elegance with timeless charm. Make this meticulously crafted retreat your own and embrace refined living at its best.
